      "insta": "https://www.instagram.com/nanditi.k"
    },
    {
      "name": "Computational Mama",
      "bio": "With a long-term experience in Exhibition Design & Museum Management, Ambika ventured into learning, teaching and experimenting with creative coding since 2017. As a co-founder of Ajaibghar and a creative technologist she combines her past expertise of art direction, museum design, and project management in arts with her computational works that are heavily inspired by generative texts, computer vision and machine learning. Her work has been featured in Casey Reas’ (co-founder Processing) recent list of generative artists doing inspiring work. She is a livestreamer on Twitch, creating inclusive spaces and learning opportunities for womxn makers to explore creative computation.",
