    "content": "Ajaibghar builds product and strategic solutions in Arts & Culture, driven by creative technology and new media. We have a background in museums, events, art direction, design, music, with expertise in cultural strategy, arts programming, project management, digital experiences. We bring exciting interventions in creative fields/arts & culture with our experience in technology, covering creative coding, product management, and digital content/marketing."
